<h3 style="margin-top: 0px">III.CANCELLATION POLICIES</h3>
<h3>2. Cancellation procedure</h3>
<ol class="tcList3">
    <li>All cancellations must be made in writing via email or fax.</li>
    <li>Please request a written confirmation back from us aknowledging such cancellation. You must expect a reply from one of our reservations executives on the same day. This confirmation will work as your guarantee that we have received the cancellation on that day.</li>
    <li>Cancellation costs are calculated based on the date that Costa Rica Reps receives the actual cancellation in writing, minus any other guarantee deposit to hotels, local flights and service providers which are non-refundable based on their own cancellation policies.</li>
</ol>